quote.summary: E-House China Enterprise Holdings Ltd is a company mainly engaged in real estate transaction services. The Company conducts its operations through four segments. The Real Estate Agency Services in the Primary Market segment includes e formulating and executing marketing and sales strategies for real estate projects developed by real estate developers, promoting the projects to prospective purchasers, and facilitating sales transactions. The Real Estate Data and Consulting Services segment provides various data services, real estate rating and ranking services, and real estate consulting services. The Real Estate Brokerage Network Services segment provides second-hand housing brokerage network services and assists property developer customers to expand sales channels. The Digital Marketing Services segment provides e-commerce services, online advertising services and listing services. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic markets.
